    <releaseNotes>
### Added
- Allow components to specify Java agents and JVM arguments
- Add support for Quilt loader
- Add buttons to Matrix space and Reddit
- Allow moving toolbars
- Add Quit after game stop option
- Block game launch if Java is incompatible
- Add grayscale icon for monochrome icon themes
- Track and display game world sizes
- Add more detailed progress dialog for mod-downloader
- Add version selector for Technic modpacks
- Add basic filtering to mod downloader
- Lay groundwork for ARM64 support
- Add mod loader selection to instance creation
- Save custom offline player name
- Add optional menu-bar and keyboard navigation
- [Linux] Provide portable builds
- [Windows] Add support for POLYMC_JAVA_PATHS

### Changed
- Improve mod downloader
- Switch logo font to Josefin Sans
- Updated Nix Flake
- Combine portable and system builds
- Build script improvements
- Update credits and branding
- Update license for logos
- Change path of help pages
- Use system libraries if possible
- [macOS] Switch to Qt 5.15.3

### Fixed
- Fix and improve translatable strings
- Switch to newer Discord logo
- [Linux] Flatpak fixes
- [Linux] Install missing manpage
- [FreeBSD] Force system LWJGL natives

### Removed
- Remove unused notification system

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/PolyMC/PolyMC/compare/1.1.1...1.2.0
